description: This screenshot from the Vegas rally and New Trump ad!!! She in the Q shirt appears at the 55 sec mark. Five by five is the predecessor to the term ""Loud and Clear"" or ""Lima/Charlie"" used by military units today. It found its way into verbal slang, meaning ""everything is good"" or ""everybody is well/good"". Used often by Q as 5:5.  Link to ad: https://twitter.com/JeffDeRiso/status/1233203378060218368?s=20  Yay!
